    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for the declared model risk level. Uncertainty quantification demonstrates NIH prediction uncertainty of ±12.3% at 95% confidence, within the 25% output comparison acceptance band. The UQ technical report references a screening sensitivity study identifying dominant input drivers; formal structured sensitivity analysis linkage to this package is deferred but the verbal characterization in the UQ narrative is considered sufficient for Medium assurance at MRL 2. Decision: Accepted for use in CPB hemolysis worst-case identification.",
